padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; padding-top: 0px; \"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/4bb17e9dgw1e4pw56zonxj20oz0gidke.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: initial; border-left-color: initial; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; padding-top: 0px; \"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p><p><b><font size=\"5\">全球人民2013年5月25日《反对孟山都进军》使命宣言</font></b></p><p><font size=\"3\">原载：</font><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4bb17e9d0102e7rc.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 50, 101); text-decoration: none; \">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4bb17e9d0102e7rc.html</a></p><p><br></p><p><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr></span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: red; \">我们为什么举行《反对孟山都进军》？</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">1</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）试验研究表明孟山都的转基因食品可以导致严重的健康状况，如癌症肿瘤、不孕不育与生育缺陷。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">2</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）在美国，食品与药物管理署（</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">FDA</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">），被赋予为美国人民保证食品安全的使命，受到前孟山都管理人员的操控，我们感到这是一种有疑问的利益冲突，可以解释为什么缺乏政府领导的对转基因产品长期影响的研究。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">3</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）最近，美国国会与总统与其他东西一起通过了外号为“孟山都保护法”的附加条款，禁止法院停止孟山都转基因种子的销售。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">4</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）已经太长时间，孟山都一直是公司补贴与政治偏袒的受益者。有机农民与小型农民遭到损失而孟山都继续加强他们对于世界食品供应的垄断，包括独家对于种子与遗传结构的专利。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">5</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）孟山都的转基因种子有害于环境；例如，科学家们已经显示孟山都的转基因种子是造成世界蜜蜂“蜂群衰竭失调”的原因之一。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: red; \">我们提倡什么样的解决办法？</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">1</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）用你们购买食品的美元进行投票：购买有机产品与抵制孟山都拥有的在他们产品中使用转基因成分的产品。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">2</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）对转基因食品进行标识，使消费者可以更容易做出知情的决定。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">3</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）废除美国的“孟山都保护法”的相关条款。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">4</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）呼吁对转基因的健康影响做进一步的科学研究。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">5</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）通过直接通讯、基层新闻业、社会媒体等让孟山都的主管与支持孟山都的政治家们承担责任。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">6</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）继续将孟山都的秘密告知公众。</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Georgia; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">7</span></b><b style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); \">）走上街头向世界与孟山都表明我们不会默认这些非正义。我们不容忍任用亲信。我们不容忍毒药。这就是为什么我们举行反对孟山都进军！</span></b><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: simsun; line-height: 24px; text-align: left; \">&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/4bb17e9dgw1e4qo6xfirzj20hb0qoad5.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: initial; border-left-color: initial; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; padding-top: 0px; \"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/4bb17e9dgw1e4qy3niy1aj20q30i9ted.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: initial; border-left-color: initial; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-right-