E_D("replace into `supe_postmessages` values('12373','0','12373','<font size=\"3\"><b>&nbsp;【社科院副院长李慎明】“中国梦”与中国特色社会主义</b></font><div><font size=\"3\">——毛泽东的“三个世界”理论没有过时</font><div><font size=\"3\"> &nbsp;<br><embed src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNTYxOTUzNTQw/v.swf\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" quality=\"high\" width=\"730\" height=\"500\" align=\"middle\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"></font></div><div><font size=\"3\"><br></font></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2012年11月，习近平同志在参观《复兴之路》的时候提出了“中国梦”这个概念，他说：“实现中华民族伟大复兴就是中华民族近代以来最伟大的梦想”。接着1月5号在党校的讲话里面，他在归纳十八大报告精神的时候说：“说一千道一万，十八大精神归根结底为一点：坚持和发展中国特色社会主义”。这就出现了两个概念，一个是中国梦，一个是中国特色社会主义。那么两者之间的关系是什么？中国梦提法的由来、内涵与精神实质是什么？为什么说实现中国梦的关键是坚持和发展中国特色社会主义？本期报告中国社会科学院副院长李慎明为您精彩解读《中国梦与中中国特色社会主义》。</font></kbd></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></kbd></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b>主要内容：</b></span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">一、中国梦提法的由来、内涵与精神实质</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（一）由来；</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（二）中国梦的内涵与精神实质；</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（三）中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦与中国特色社会主义的关系；</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（四）中国梦与其他国家梦的关系。</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">二、实现中国梦的关键是坚持和发展中国特色社会主义</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（一）什么叫中国特色社会主义？</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（二）什么是中国特色社会主义道路？</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（三）中国特色社会主义理论体系；</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（四）中国特色制度。</span>\r\n</font></kbd></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b>三、实现中国梦所面临的国内外的机遇和挑战</b></span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（一）目前值得我们高度关注的国内外问题有哪些？</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">1.国际方面</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">2.国内方面：房价、财政收入</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b>（二）国际现状和趋势</b></span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">1.和平发展合作仍然是当今时代的潮流</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">2.世界多极化和经济全球化趋势继续深化</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">3.科技革命迅猛发展</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">4.美国的雄心太大</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">5.国际金融危机仍未见底</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">6.世界社会主义思潮开始有所复兴</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">7.世界上可利用的矛盾很多</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">8.美国等西方国家有求于我们</span>\r\n</font></kbd></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b>三、实现中国梦所面临的国内外的机遇和挑战</