ht: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">5.市场资源</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">6.劳动力资源</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">7.外资</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">四、坚持和发展中国特色社会主义，为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦而奋斗</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（一）全党、全国的角度看怎么做？</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \"><span style=\"font-family: arial, ''Arial Narrow''; line-height: 28px; \">（二）公民、党员、干部的个人角度怎么做？</span></font>\r\n</kbd></div><div><font face=\"arial, ''Arial Narrow''\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">……</span></font></div><div><font face=\"arial, ''Arial Narrow''\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><br></span></font></div><div><kbd class=\"showvideo\" title=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XNTYxOTUzNTQw.html\"><div style=\"border-bottom-width: 0px; border-bottom-style: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: initial; border-left-color: initial; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-width: 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 27px; \"><fon