al; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">本来在王景同志的一再【关照】下，不想再说什么了。但想想，人长了一张嘴，除了【吃饭】，还得【说话】<font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">何况到了我这个年纪的人，【吃饭】已经有限了，【说话】也不用多【顾虑】了，爱咋咋吧！</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">1<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，感谢美华君不懈的工作！【既要不断工作】【也要注意身体】，该休息的时候还是需要休息。</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">2<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，对【习】的态度，我再次重申：（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">1</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">）支持（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">2</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">）继续观察。</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">3<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，【审</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">BO</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">】的事情是【必然】的，诸位大可不必【愤怒与失望】。因为这一件事情是上一届就【完全确定】的事情，怎么可能有【突然逆转】的【半点】呢？换上谁也没有办法</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">-----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">除非撕破脸，对着干</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">但这样的【时机】到了吗？</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">4<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">【审</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">BO</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">】的【后果】是社会民意【进一步分裂】，但我觉得【乱】是【乱不起来】的！我不相信，当今社会中会真的有人【起来造反】！</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">无论是多么【革命和马列毛】，依然只能在【网络】上【发表点看法而已】</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">-----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">这一点，历届【当局】都【洞若观火】</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">切准了【左派的命脉】嘀。</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">5<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，什么时候会真的【乱】，真的【革命与造反】？我看至少需要两个基本条件：（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">1</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">）【民不聊生】（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">2</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">）【大多数年轻人觉悟】，这两条，现在一条也不成熟，所以不管怎么【折腾】，还是没戏！</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">6<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，然而，造成这两条条件的客观环境是存在的</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">-----</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">如果不走【前山城路线】，我估计大概十年之内，肯定会出现。所以【习总】【任重道远】，好自为之吧！</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \">&nbsp;<wbr></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; text-indent: 21pt; \"><span style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; \">7<font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">，【审</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">BO</font><font face=\"宋体\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; \">】之后，如果能再打出几只【口才大老虎】或者【卖国大老虎】，大概可以【平衡一下民意】，否则【失望度】将激增！</font></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; 