FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">。文章标题说：美国军方跟踪监视反转人士和独立科学家，美国军方为什么要淌转基因的浑水呢？看完文章自会明白。</SPAN></STRONG><STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">文中几处谈到了专业黑客网络攻击，对此，我也有一定的感受。我揭露转毒基因的巨大危害和转毒基因骗子集团数不胜数的弥天大谎已经</SPAN></STRONG><STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年多了，如果说转基因骗子集团没有对我的电脑感兴趣，恐怕它们自己都不会承认，以前是电脑偶尔感染木马病毒，但很容易被我的顶级杀木马软件给查杀了，但前几天出现了一个让我头疼、连顶级杀毒软件也没办法的木马，安装在电脑系统文件</SPAN></STRONG><STRONG><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">tcpip</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">里面，杀毒软件也不敢查杀，因为一旦删除文件，就会造成系统崩溃、蓝屏、不能上网等严重问题。不过，经过几个小时的折腾，终于把这个我第一次遇上的深度隐藏木马消灭了！我的感觉是：这不是一般的黑客所为，因为我最近打击猛散毒和中国转基因骗子集团、批评黑皮助纣为虐阻挠反转基因活动的文章都很麻辣。所以，在此提醒全国的反转人士、爱国人士注意自己电脑的安全。</SPAN></STRONG><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">美国军方跟踪监视反转基因运动人士和独立科学家</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">《可持续脉搏网》</SPAN><st1:chsdate Year=\"2013\" Month=\"7\" Day=\"13\" IsLunarDate=\"False\" IsROCDate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2013</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">13</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">[</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">编辑</SPAN><SPAN style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">]<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">德国最大的报纸《南德意志报》今天公布了一篇令人震惊的文章，揭示了猛散毒、美国军方和美国政府是如何跟踪监视反转基因运动人士和研究转基因生物危害的独立科学家。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">在一个非常详细的文章，《南德意志报》记者在文章里以猛散毒为例，详细讲述了美国政府是如何“推进企业利益”的。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">以下是全文内容：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">文章指出：“值得注意的是，任何批评猛散毒公司的人要么被迫生活举步维艰，要么一只无形的大手结束了他们的的职业生涯。但是，这个“任何人”是谁呢？目标是类似澳大利亚的朱迪·卡曼这类科学家。她因为研究转基因生物而出名</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>......</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">因此，一些发表了卡曼研究结果的网站经常成为黑客攻击的目标</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB> - IP</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">协议比对表明，不仅猛散毒定期跟踪这些网站的页面，但还有美国政府的不同机构，包括军方。这些包括<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">海军网络信息中心</B>，<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">美国联邦航空管理局</B>和<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">美国的陆军情报中心</B></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>...</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">猛散毒对研究感兴趣，卡曼博士表示理解。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">她说：“但我不明白，为什么美国政府和军方要监视我。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">文章的结论是：“一大批孟山都的批评者报告说他们受到专业黑客的定期攻击</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>...</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">叛逃者爱德华·斯诺顿也指出了情报部门的行动和经济活动之间的联系。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">在详细介绍猛散毒及其和与美国政府和黑水保安公司的联系后，《南德意志报》问道：“战争允许采用一切手段吗？在新一轮的网络战争中更是如此吗？”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"><BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">点击这里查看更多有关朱迪·卡曼博士和她的研究工作信息，包括她对转基因饲料对猪的危害的最新研究。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>www</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">点</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>gmojudycarman</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\">点</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>org/<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB>US Military Tracks GMO Campaigners and Independent Scientists</SPAN></STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><BR>Sustainable Pulse, July 13 2013 [edited]<BR><BR>The largest German daily newspaper Süddeutsche Zeitung has today published a shocking article that reveals how Monsanto, the US Military and the <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">US</st1:place></st1:country-region> government track both anti-GMO Campaigners and Independent Scientists who study the dangers of GMOs.<BR><BR>In a very detailed article the Süddeutsche Zeitung journalists reveal information on how the US Government “advances the interests of their corporations” using Monsanto as an example.<BR><BR>[Read The Full Article Below]<BR><BR>The article states: “It is noticeable that anyone who criticizes Monsanto has their life made very difficult or an invisible hand ends their careers. But who is this Anyone? Targets are scientists such as the Australian Judy Carman. She has made a name for herself with studies of genetically modified organisms…. Thus, several websites on which Carman published her studies are regularly the target of hacker attacks – Evaluations of IP protocols show that not only Monsanto regularly tracks the pages of these sites, but also various institutions of the <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">U.S.</st1:place></st1:country-region> government, including the military. These include the <st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">Navy</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">Network</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">Information</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceType w:st=\"on\">Center</st1:PlaceType>, the Federal Aviation Administration and the <st1:place w:st=\"on\"><st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">United States</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">Army</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st=\"on\">Intelligence</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceType w:st=\"on\">Center</st1:PlaceType></st1:place>…”<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB\" lang=EN-GB><BR>That Monsanto is interested in the studies, is understandable for Dr. Carman. “But I do not understand why the <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">U.S.</st1:place></st1:country-region> government and the military is watching me,” she says.”<BR><BR>The article concludes: “A conspicuous number of Monsanto critics report regular attacks by professional hackers… The Whistleblower Edward Snowden has pointed to the connection between actions of the intelligence services and the activities of the economy.”<BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"><BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\" lang=EN-GB>After a very detailed introduction into Monsanto and their links to the <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">US</st1:place></st1:country-region> government and the security firm Blackwater, Süddeutsche Zeitung asks the question: \"Is everything allowed in war? Especially in the new-fangled cyber war?\"<BR><BR>Visit here for more information on Dr. Judy Carman and her work including her latest study on GM Feed and Pigs<BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"><BR style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\"></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>','a:5:{i:0;s:8:\"生物武器\";i:1;s:6:\"转基因\";i:2;s:10:\"转基因大豆\";i:3;s:10:\"转基因食品\";i:4;s:10:\"转基因玉米\";}','120.13.67.61','','0','','美国	转基因	生物武器	军事	世界	中国政府	农业部	中国	国际	中华民族	战略	媒体	汉奸	民族	老百姓	战争	正义	网络	活动	经济	工作','半解一知半解','作者新浪博客','','http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4c5581460101g1cn.html','0');");
