E_D("replace into `supe_postmessages` values('15668','0','15668','<P align=center><STRONG><FONT size=6><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">祖国啊我是追寻你的儿子<BR>沐俗</SPAN></FONT></STRONG></P>\r\n<P align=center><STRONG><FONT size=6><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"></SPAN></FONT></STRONG><STRONG><FONT size=6><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">二零一三年北京春天的风很冷，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">我好像幽灵一般飘到了天安门前。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">二零一三年北京春天雨也很冷，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">它会慢慢地浇凉了整个金水桥面。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">二零一三年的春天让我又忆起，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">我愿用我生命来镌刻的那段思念。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">城市的风是那么的压抑和弱小，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">没力气摇动红旗让它高高地飘扬。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">悲愤的雨一时间都化作了泪水，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">滴进了我这颗孤绝又凄凉的心房。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">今天我站在长安街上仰面哭泣，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">因为我想起了我离去多年的爹娘。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">父亲啊我的祖国我永远忘不了，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">那年你在我身前对抗豺狼的背影。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">母亲啊我的祖国我永远忘不了，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">那年你饿着肚子省给儿吃的菜饼。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">忘不了我的爹娘就埋葬在这里，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">埋葬在这三十七年前日落的山顶。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">爹啊你知不知道走后的日子里，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">他们拿走了你曾经耕耘过的梯田。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">你的儿子如今只能替他们打工，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">还种着当年爹整理过的那片菜园。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">只是曾修好的水库现在荒废了，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">不用化肥连土地都对人装作寒酸。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">娘啊你知不知道走后的日子里，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">咱家的叔伯妯娌全都与他们合伙。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">暗地里一起拒绝卖给儿子棉花，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">没有冬衣他们讥笑儿的衣裳破落。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">现在妯娌都住上了他们盖的房，</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN class=edit_font_normal style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px SimSun, Verdana, sans-serif; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">叔伯也各自在他们建的厂里干活。</SPAN><BR style=\"WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: 14px/24px 宋体; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(212,224,236); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><BR style=\"WORD-SPA