e; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN class=Apple-converted-space>&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">幸福树生态房的发明，充分验证了马克思主义的人类社会螺旋式上升理论的真理性。人类从树上下来，又要回到树上，完成了人类生活方式的第一次质的飞跃和螺旋式上升。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 25px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<FONT style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 32px\" size=4>近年来，中国及世界上的大部分地区，特别是北京等大城市，空气污染、土地污染、水污染、食品污染、地震洪水飓风等天灾人祸日渐频繁，道德滑坡、信仰缺失日趋严重，特别是污染企业排放的化学气体、有毒气体携带毒气、病菌所造成的癌症、各类传染病、职业病等频发，给人民群众的生命安全、财产安全、饮食安全、身体健康造成严重威胁，幸福树生态养生房的发明不但彻底解决了上述所有问题，而且还可以帮助人民群众得到共同健康、共同富裕、共同觉悟的幸福新生活，顺利实现中国人民的幸福生活中国梦。</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 25px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">幸福树多功能生态房，像一棵大果树，我们人类不远的将来就是要生活在这样的幸福树上。住在这样的房子里，在自然环境日益恶劣的未来世界，人类的生命安全、身体健康和财产安全将得到彻底、充分的保障。幸福树生态房房顶就是一个高效率、高科技的现代生态农场，为群众的食品安全和养殖、种植创富提供了平台，其室内红绿蓝信仰体系的配置，更是实现全民觉悟的平台。幸福树生态房的大面积推广，将使中国人民共同健康、共同富裕、共同觉悟的幸福生活中国梦变的触手可及。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">据悉，邯郸市的有识之士、部分房产行业的先行者正在与幸福树生态房技术方---幸福航母进行接触、洽谈，如果谈判顺利，人类未来的居所<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">---</SPAN>幸福树有可能在<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">2013</SPAN>年国庆节前夕在邯郸首度现身。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\">作者：崔士忠</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2013.7.27</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">幸福树生态房简介：<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">一、主要功能：<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">、防水、防火、防烟、防震。幸福树生态房可以自由浮动上下几米的距离，可以有效防御大火、烟雾及有毒气体的排放和蔓延，不怕任何级别的地震．雨水１００％完全收集于屋顶用于种植蔬菜和经济作物；三套通风系统，无须传统空调、抽油烟机，就能有效防控<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">pm2.5</SPAN>以上重污染有毒空气及以空气作为媒介的传染病、化学气体污染致病的发生，有效遏制癌症、禽流感等污染病症的进一步扩散和蔓延。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">、空间舒适，节能环保，可以自己发电。幸福树生态房通风透光性能非常良好．具有节水节电舒适的特点．适合一切需要房屋的城市和农村，无需电扇空调采暖设施即可冬暖夏凉，完全的生态低耗住宅和低碳新生活。幸福树生态房可以整体３６０度自由转动，自动跟踪太阳转动以最大程度吸收光能。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">3</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">、生态食品自给，红绿蓝新文化给予觉悟和正能量：幸福树生态养生房楼顶是现代化高科技高级生态农场，并配备养殖间沼气发电和污水处理设施．是一个天然的高科技生态种植、养殖场，可以用于种植、养殖绿色有机食品和经济作物等，生态、绿色、安全、非转基因的蔬菜、瓜果、禽蛋肉类、粮食等可以自给自足，种植经济作物还可以赢利共富。屋内根据中国传统文化设置摆件和字画，给居住人以觉悟和正能量，实现元气自养、疾病自疗、生命自控、智慧自觉、性命双修，是幸福航母实现三个幸福计划：“全民健康计划、全民共富计划、全民觉悟计划”的有效项目载体之一。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">4</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">、造价低，成本费用与普通民房基本持平。生态房造价低廉，与普通民房的造价基本持平，业主若要求增加其他功能，需要适当追加投资。每平方米造价在<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">1800</SPAN>元左右。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">5</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">、前期可以作为旅游景点、集镇的观光旅游体验赢利项目。前期可以作为未来人类居所的观光旅游体验项目，为投资者创造可观利润，也可以用于中国梦想园即幸福航母生态信仰园建设。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">二、必然趋势和人类住宅革命<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 35pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">幸福树多功能生态养生房对土地质量要求不高，可以有效缓解建筑与粮食争地困局。随着该项目的大面积推广，还将逐步为国家解放出上百万平方公里的优质土地，以取代基本良田的作用，是地方政府摆脱土地财政的有效措施。幸福航母幸福树生态房作为我们现在房屋的更新换代产品和新的利润增长点已成必然趋势，它的大面积推广将会彻底颠覆现有建筑的传统思维成为新的住宅领航和商业导向，引起一场人类居住的革命。人类从树上来，再回到树上去，完成了更加高级的良性循环。<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">三、幸福树工作原理<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 49pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">幸福树生态房全名：幸福航母幸福树新型实用浮仓悬挂式整体自由转动升降抗震减灾节能环保生态养生建筑，主要结构包括基座、位于基座上的压载仓。基座与压载仓为分体结构，压载仓内悬设有浮体，浮体的上端连接有悬挂框，悬挂框的外侧和顶端安装有由多个房屋组成的楼体，悬挂框内设有第一进气口以及与房屋连通的第一进气通道，悬挂框的内侧通过可调弹性支承座连接旋转轴，旋转轴的两端固定有弹性轮，弹性轮与压载仓抵接，所述浮体的下端设置有防偏平衡仓。幸福航母生态房将由多个房屋组成的楼体设于压载仓外，使得每个房屋的采光性和通风性良好，提高了人们生活环境的舒适度，且基座与压载仓之间填充有润滑剂，压载仓可在基座上滑动，以达到抗震减灾效果。（附图）<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">&nbsp;<SPAN class=Apple-converted-space>&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\">图片网址：<SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"WHITE-SPACE: normal; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; WORD-SPACING: 0px; COLOR: rgb(153,138,98); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 14px/25px Arial, Helvetica, simsun, u5b8bu4f53; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px 0px 10px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(254,254,253); TEXT-INDENT: 7pt; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\"><A style=\"COLOR: rgb(196,163,12); TEXT-DECORATION: none; LINE-HEIGHT: 34px\" href=\"http://cuisz1223.blog.163.com/blog/static/4262952013614113633821/\">http://cuisz1223.blog.163.com/blog/static/4262952013614113633821/</A>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>','a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"邯郸\";}','110.248.241.102','','0','','邯郸	马克思	中国	世界	北京	中国人	中国梦	经济	转基因	工作','崔士忠','幸福航母','','','0');");
E_D("replace into `supe_postmessages` values('15695','0','15695','<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万俟卨</SPAN><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> </FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">从接案的那一刻</SPAN><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"> </FONT><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">你已经遗臭万年</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><FONT size=3>岳喜源</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在这个世界上，总有一些小人、恶人、佞臣、奸党，为了自己升官发财及本集团的利益，依附于邪恶卖国投降势力，以各种莫须有的罪名，诬陷暗害正直君子、爱国人士、忠良贤臣，万俟卨就是这样一个大恶之佞臣，他为了升官发财，依附于秦桧的投降卖国势力，<SPAN style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\">高宗绍兴十一年（</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1141</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年）秉承秦桧意旨，弹劾岳飞，主治岳飞之狱。诬陷岳飞虚报军情及逗留淮西等罪，一口咬定岳云曾经写信给张宪，布置夺军谋反的计划，陷</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><A href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/2545.htm\" target=_blank><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT color=#136ec2>岳飞</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">于死狱，致使岳飞父子和张宪等以</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><A href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/48122.htm\" target=_blank><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT color=#136ec2>莫须有</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">的罪名被杀害。万俟卨，如果你不接岳飞的案子，还可以青史留名，可你却偏偏接了岳飞的案子，以种种伪证诬陷陷害岳飞，致使岳飞被残杀在风波亭，可以说，从接案的那一刻，你万俟卨已经走上了与人民为敌的邪恶道路，已经要遗臭万年了，杭州西子湖畔的岳飞庙前，你将永远长跪下去，你的龌蹉灵魂已经被绑在了历史的耻辱柱上，遭万世唾骂。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">我们不得不承认，秦桧及万俟卨侥幸逃脱了当时人民的审判，这和当时科技的不发达及人民的愚昧有着很大关系，但他们都没有逃脱后人的审判，还是长跪在了岳飞庙前，历史发展到了今天，科技的发达及人民的大批觉醒，要想再制造冤假错案，栽脏陷害，诬陷诽谤，捏造伪证，已经是不可能了，纸里包不住火，很快就会被人们识破的，要想侥幸逃脱人民的审判，已经是不可能了。尤其是网络革命的迅速兴起，更使那些陷害忠良的卑鄙小人难以逃脱人民的审判，穆巴拉克及卡扎菲都难以幸免遇难，更何况这些无耻的小人哪。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">岳飞被杀害后，人民是敢怒而不敢言，因为有秦桧的高压政策，他把老百姓的嘴堵上了，有为岳飞喊冤者，要处死刑，可是就是有人对秦桧看不惯，你秦桧就是一个投降卖国者，残害忠良，不得人心，你不让我说话，我可有革命的权利，这个人就是殿前校尉施全，他愤然行刺秦桧，虽然刺杀秦桧没有成功，但却让秦桧出了一身冷汗，从此以后，常病不起，呜呼哀哉了。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">我们今天的人民，饱受了官僚资产阶级、殖民资产阶级及大资产阶级的残酷剥削和压迫，人民已经普遍觉醒，毛浙东思想正成为他们战斗的武器，一切残害忠良制造冤假错案的卑鄙小人，都将不会逃脱</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">13</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿人民的审判。那一刻，不会太远，也许，就近在眼前。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">你可以封网堵嘴，也可以用恐吓来威胁，也可以用逮捕、坐牢及杀头来扼杀正义力量，可是，人民的思想，你们是永远封杀不了的，它不在沉默中灭亡，便会在沉默中爆发。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">太行爱国力量</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2012.08.10<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>','a:0:{}','182.112.117.130','','0','','世界	历史	网络	老百姓	资产阶级	正义','岳喜源','自创','','','0');");
E_D("replace into `supe_postmessages` values('15696','0','15696','<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal align=center><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 22pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一个家庭的被迫害史</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">家庭概况：王某，男，某省某县某村农民，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年生，配偶杨某</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1970</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年生，我俩于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1991</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年结婚。长女</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1992</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年生，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2004</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年被推入水溺水身亡（公安机关不予立案），母亲受此打击，不久去世。现家里还有长子和次女，子女户籍年龄均比实际年龄大出</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">—</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">岁（长期申诉不予修正）。父亲王某，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1914</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年生，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年受诬告被捕入狱，后惨死监狱（家属未收到任何通知），长期未得到平反。自</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1980</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年代起，本人向各级权力机关部门申诉要求平反，自此各种迫害案件接踵而来，但很多事实清楚、证据确凿的案件都没有得到公正判决，甚至不予立案。致使，整个家庭长期处于恐怖迫害阴影中。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">父亲王某被诬告反革命罪惨死监狱案（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">—</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（一）案情简况</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">生父王某，生于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1914</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年，农民。解放前勤恳务农，偶尔做点小本生意，购有几亩薄田，通过诚实劳动虽然艰辛，但较其他家庭，生活能自给自足，在全民性贫苦的旧社会农村，这样的生活令当地其他更贫困的村民眼红。解放后，被划为中农，仅仅是有够维持家庭生计的土地，靠劳动自食其力。当时生父响应党和国家的号召，无条件将田产交由集体所有。因此，被党和国家信任，由其担任村小组长。为了感激党和国家的信任，生父坚持实事求是的原则，反对村里其他村干部虚报收成、私吞公共财产的行为，因此被这些人怀恨在心，于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1957</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日晚，制造火灾现场并诬告是生父所为，生父由此被捕入狱。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">因为此事不是生父所为，审讯时，生父坚决否认，同时，审判机关认为当时火灾并未造成损失，构不成诬告者企图诬告的纵火罪，有望很快释放出狱。诬告者打探到此消息后认为生父出狱会对他们进行报复，必先将其整死在监狱。因此，他们作假证诬告生父窝藏匪首，至此，一桩普通案件性质发生巨大变化，变成反革命罪。此后，生父在被关押期间惨死监狱，但相关部门从未通知家属，至今家属不知其为何年何月何日因何事去世，也不知其遗体下落。（案情具体情况见附件）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（二）申诉经过</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">改革开放前，这件事一直没有机会申诉，改革开放后，国家开始全面平反冤假错案，我家才看到了希望，于</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1980</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年向台法院信访室要求对生父案件复查，县法院信访室答复：“你为提出申诉收悉，按法律程序，案件尚未经我院判刑，不属我们复查，我们已将你的申诉转交公安局，请以后与他们联系。至于房子被收的问题，是哪级处理的，由哪级负责落实，请与有关单位联系。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1981</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日并有公章”。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">由此可见，生父是在关押侦查阶段去世，但具体是什么时候因为什么原因，死者家属从未收到来自公检法方面的书面通知或口头通知。于是，家属要求县公安局重新侦查审理。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1982</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年收到县法院通知书，通知书提到：“申诉人元对原人民法院一九五七年法刑字第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>36</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号判决不服，提出申诉，要求对其父的犯罪事实复查纠正。……本院维持一九五七年十一月五日（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>57</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">）刑法字第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>36</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号判决，特此驳回。”</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至此可见，在短短的两年时间内，同一个法院对同一个案件给出了两个截然不同的结论。生父被关押审讯到什么阶段权力机关必须给出一个符合事实、令人信服的真相。为此，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1986</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1987</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1988</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年多次申诉，</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1988</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日县人民法院仍然维持原判，其中提及“二王系被告（因反革命罪纵火案，判处死刑，缓刑二年，强迫劳动，以观后效）之子”，这是家属第一次得知父亲惨死监狱的官方文件。见附件。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">从上面叙述可以推断出案情发展的基本脉络：生父被诬陷纵火（证据不足）——诬陷生父通匪（侦查审理）——生父在关押期间被迫害死亡（大概</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1959</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年前后，大跃进，左倾），显然是个冤案。本案件有着深刻的历史背景，与大跃进前期社会上出现的左倾路线不无关系，应该得到平反。但是</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1982</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">和</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1988</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年县法院两次驳回申诉，维持子虚乌有的原判。致使本人多次上访请求权力机关给予公正判决。在申诉过程中，当地公检法及行政机关工作人员公然宣称，这个案件是我县最大的历史冤案，但不能给你家平反，因为这样会给我们县的公检法抹黑，中国解放</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>60</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年，就是不让你家解放。这种知错不改、视法律权威于不顾、不保护人民生命财产安全等合法权益的行为是对国家尊严的蔑视和对国家法律公然践踏，希望得到法律制裁。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（三）该案疑点及家属诉求</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、县法院前后不到两年的时间作出的结论截然相反，这是什么原因呢？是不是滥用职权呢？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、一九五七年刑法字第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>36</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号原件在哪里呢？死刑这么重大的判决为什么不通知也不送达被告方家属呢？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、纵火案的真犯是谁？公安机关是否只听一面之词，没有全面调查？权力机关是否涉嫌滥用职权、职务犯罪？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、生父亲一介农夫，解放前并未任伪禄长、某事变中队长，请法院拿出证据；</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、生母前去探监时生父曾对她说：“我被他们诬告了，他们强迫我按手印，要把我往死里整。”到底“他们”是指谁？生父是否遭到刑讯逼供？</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、生父遗体下落呢？要求公检法寻找生父遗体下落，移交死者亲属安葬，以告慰死者亡灵，安慰死者后人。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">种种疑问和迹象表明，地方权力机关过渡介入，有作假证、采用假证词、刑讯逼供、补假文、知错不改等嫌疑。根据《中华人民共和国新刑事诉讼法》第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>242</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>243</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">条及《中华人民共和国刑事诉讼法及司法解释》（</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2012</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">）第</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>375</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>376</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">条之规定，要求启动审判监督程序并异地复查审判，依法平反，还原历史真相，处理相关人员，申请国家赔偿。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-no-proof: yes\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = v ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" /><v:shapetype id=_x0000_t75 stroked=\"f\" filled=\"f\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" o:spt=\"75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\"><v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:connecttype=\"rect\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:extrusionok=\"f\"></v:path><o:lock aspectratio=\"t\" v:ext=\"edit\"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape style=\"WIDTH: 415.5pt; HEIGHT: 554.25pt; VISIBILITY: visible; mso-wrap-style: square\" id=图片_x0020_1 type=\"#_x0000_t75\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1031\"><v:imagedata o:title=\"1\" src=\"http://www.szhgh.com/file:///C:\\\\Users\\\\ADMINI~1\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Temp\\\\msohtmlclip1\\\\01\\\\clip_image001.jpg\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"mso-no-proof: yes\" lang=EN-US><v:shape style=\"WIDTH: 415.5pt; HEIGHT: 312pt; VISIBILITY: visible; mso-wrap-style: square\" id=图片_x0020_2 type=\"#_x0000_t75\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1030\"><v:imagedata o:title=\"2\" src=\"http://www.szhgh.com/file:///C:\\\\Users\\\\ADMINI~1\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Temp\\\\msohtmlclip1\\\\01\\\\clip_image003.jpg\"><F